<head>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/adicionar.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Press+Start+2P&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* Estilo geral */
        body {
            background-color: #2c2c2c;
            font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive; /* Fonte de games para todo o corpo da página */
            color: #e1e1e1;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        /* Nav bar (mantém a fonte de games) */
        .navbar {
            height: 80px; /* Altura reservada para o nav bar */
            background-color: #333;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 0 20px;
            font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive; /* Fonte de games */
            color: #fff;
        }

        /* Card principal */
        .card {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #3c3c3c, #1a1a1a);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 20px 30px;
            max-width: 800px;
            width: 90%; /* Responsividade */
            color: #f4f4f4;
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; /* Aplica a fonte 'Cinzel' somente ao card */
        }

        /* Lateral esquerda */
        .card-left {
            flex: 1;
            text-align: right;
            padding-right: 20px;
            border-right: 1px solid #555;
        }

        .card-left label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #d4af37; /* Dourado de Anor Londo */
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        /* Inputs */
        .form-control {
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #1a1a1a;
            border: 1px solid #d4af37;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 10px;
            color: #e1e1e1;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            outline: none;
        }

        .form-control:focus {
            border-color: #f4e1a1;
            box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.8);
        }

        /* Botão */
        .btn-primary {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #d4af37;
            color: #121212;
            border: none;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease, background-color 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: #b99035;
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        /* Lateral direita */
        .card-right {
            flex: 1;
            padding-left: 20px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .card-right h1 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: #d4af37;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .card-right p {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #e1e1e1;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card">
        <!-- Lado esquerdo: formulário -->
        <div class="card-left">
            <form action="/api/alter-password" method="POST">
                <label for="password">Nova Senha</label>
                <input type="password" name="password" id="password" class="form-control" placeholder="Nova Senha">
                
                <label for="password_confirmation">Confirmar Senha</label>
                <input type="password" name="password_confirmation" id="password_confirmation" class="form-control" placeholder="Confirmar Senha">

                <button type="submit" class="btn-primary">Alterar</button>
            </form>
        </div>

        <!-- Lado direito: detalhes/explicação -->
        <div class="card-right">
            <h1>Alterar Senha</h1>
            <p>Insira suas credenciais para redefinir a senha. Certifique-se de que sua nova chave seja forte e segura.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
